
BetOnCode

BC is a platform which provides coders around the world to bet on their coding skills. The winner side will win 
the money on bet.

There could be different match formats like there are in different games cricket(IPL,Test Cricket, Onday etc)

and then after this could also be organized among different countries where there would be a national coding
team of each country. and different formats of coding contests can be organized among these countries like 
with other games. 
             This will basically improve programming spirit at a very big level. Entertaining at the same time.






